title: Windows 10 Spring Creators Update EN-US x64 17134.1 RTM ISO
description: This is the RS4 Windows 10 Spring Creators Update EN-US x64 Final Release 17134.1 ISO. It replaces the 17113.1 and 17133.74 versions as the final RTM candidate. No updates will install on a clean install from this ISO except for Defender updates and the Malicious Software Tool update. If you never installed your motherboard, hardware and video drivers etc. before running Windows Update they may install as well. It has Pro and Home Windows 10 versions including the N versions. It will fit on a 4GB USB key. Download RUFUS here to make a GPT install USB. https://rufus.akeo.ie/ It is NOT cracked! You'll need to have already installed Windows 10 or have a valid license key to do a activate a clean install of this ISO. No need to illegally crack Windows 10 when you can buy a legit key on eBay for about $10. Go to MyDigitalLife forums to learn how do make this ISO yourself
